Here are the main links for each functionality in your Aramco Review Platform:

User-Facing
Home (Station Selection):
http://localhost:3000/

Login:
http://localhost:3000/login

Register:
http://localhost:3000/register

Review a Station:
http://localhost:3000/review/[stationId]
(Replace [stationId] with the actual station ID.)

Reward Page (after 5th review):
http://localhost:3000/reward/[couponCode]
(Replace [couponCode] with the actual code.)

My Rewards (see all earned coupons):
http://localhost:3000/my-rewards

Search Rewards by Phone (for users or staff):
http://localhost:3000/reward-search

Admin CRM
Admin Dashboard (analytics):
http://localhost:3000/admin/dashboard

All Reviews (sorted by station):
http://localhost:3000/admin/reviews

Staff/Station
Reward QR/Coupon Scan (claim/validate):
http://localhost:3000/reward-scan